  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887690/extras/ab7906033ce59166155e7294a31219a4.avif?t=1743142870\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887690/extras_big/ab7906033ce59166155e7294a31219a4.avif?t=1743142870 width=800 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887690/extras/d494b49be3ebd6a4c63cfc247d0f1c52.avif?t=1743142870\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887690/extras_big/d494b49be3ebd6a4c63cfc247d0f1c52.avif?t=1743142870 width=800 height=388 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What secrets lie within the moon turned into cheese? </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the world of Cheese Moon, the moon was originally just a regular moon. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, at some point in the past, for reasons unknown, <strong>the moon completely turned into cheese.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887690/extras/19d699b06b007110c606e1cc42a39a74.webp?t=1743142870\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887690/extras/19d699b06b007110c606e1cc42a39a74.poster.avif?t=1743142870\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=296 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our protagonist, a rabbit named Pio, lives on the far side of this moon. Having been forced into labor, mining cheese, they were abandoned in a wasteland for reasons unknown.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Yet, something feels off...</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887690/extras/e7d028c1933aeae22b54f5ed13ccde4c.avif?t=1743142870\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887690/extras_big/e7d028c1933aeae22b54f5ed13ccde4c.avif?t=1743142870 width=800 height=444 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our rabbits ride flying saucers, exploring the moon, battling aggressive Cheeses, and mysterious machines marked with the letters 'RTMK' as they uncover a vast conspiracy surrounding the moon and cheese.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Summon clones to take on mysterious foes! </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887690/extras/7d550d519abb95bf959be615d4bd239c.poster.avif?t=1743142870\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887690/extras/7d550d519abb95bf959be615d4bd239c.webm?t=1743142870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887690/extras/7d550d519abb95bf959be615d4bd239c.mp4?t=1743142870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887690/extras/6f2b8504e5951df579a264773633c72f.avif?t=1743142870\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887690/extras_big/6f2b8504e5951df579a264773633c72f.avif?t=1743142870 width=800 height=444 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887690/extras/534a8ad30228204b1ce59366f02bdff7.avif?t=1743142870\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887690/extras_big/534a8ad30228204b1ce59366f02bdff7.avif?t=1743142870 width=800 height=444 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cheese Moon is a story-driven adventure game where cute rabbits explore a strange world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Summon rabbit clones to clear stages and unearth the dark secrets hidden on the far side of the moon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With a total of 5 worlds, each consisting of 20 stages, <strong>there are 100 stages waiting for you.</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>More Companions Along the Way!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887690/extras/e00d01c60358efd386e332d053fd020d.avif?t=1743142870\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887690/extras_big/e00d01c60358efd386e332d053fd020d.avif?t=1743142870 width=800 height=444 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the story progresses, you'll find more and more seemingly insignificant rabbits joining you.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are a total of 11 rabbits you can team up with!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Talk to the rabbits</strong> and discover how each of them perceives and interacts with this world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887690/extras/7118b8c108bf3b8652cb065ccb69e845.avif?t=1743142870\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887690/extras_big/7118b8c108bf3b8652cb065ccb69e845.avif?t=1743142870 width=800 height=444 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887690/extras/87b65c8eaefb77bd443ca22cb560a4ce.avif?t=1743142870\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887690/extras_big/87b65c8eaefb77bd443ca22cb560a4ce.avif?t=1743142870 width=800 height=444 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our protagonist, the rabbit Pio, along with their companions, will gradually get closer to the mysterious truth.   <br>Combine the rabbits, each with their own personalities and abilities, appropriately to overcome the enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i></i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887690/extras/e301a526e9bf22446f1104cb6e5b1b70.poster.avif?t=1743142870\" width=800 height=303 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887690/extras/e301a526e9bf22446f1104cb6e5b1b70.webm?t=1743142870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><i></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>What is Cheese? What is a rabbit?  </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>What are these mysterious machines working for?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>The answers lie within the world of the Cheese Moon, waiting for you to uncover them...</i></strong></p>",
